{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7e388aa77e","title":"在延安各界欢迎全国感劳总会北路感劳团晚会上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"df06cd2ced","index":0,"year":1945,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"7e388aa77e"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji20","name":"毛泽东全集第20卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji20.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji20":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f728a4c4b5","type":"paragraph","text":"在延安各界欢迎全国感劳总会北路感劳团晚会上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"7e388aa77e"},{"id":"d423f02ff6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年）我们要做亲者快优者痛的事，而为亲者所痛优者所快的事一件也不做。我们要站定自己的立场，决不能与敌人的口号混同起来我们的口号是要处处与敌人对立，决不能有丝毫与敌人混同，一切与敌人相同的言论都是助敌张目的滋调，任何人想要肩起敌人的口号而又言抗敌，那只是欺人之谈，残酷的历史将给予严厉的证明","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"7e388aa77e"},{"id":"5c43e38072","type":"paragraph","text":"中乐1945年，毛泽东在延安。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"7e388aa77e"}],"page":{"id":"d4504c35d5","publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"7e388aa77e","start":149,"end":150}}}},"__N_SSG":true}